name: Digital Goods: Multi-Category
description:
Merchants that sell at least two of the following specified digital
products:
• MCC 5815 (Digital Goods: Audiovisual Media Including Books,
Movies, and Music)
• MCC 5816 (Digital Goods: Games)
• MCC 5817 (Digital Goods: Software Applications [Excluding
Games])
A digital good is electronically transferred to the purchaser and
obtained by means other than tangible storage media.
